history.content:
Do you want to make an impact on the Berkeley tech community? Do you want to lead projects related to diversity and representation, mental health resources, more?

 

The ASUC Office of Senator Maddy Chen is looking for a Tech Director, Data Science Director, and Civic Tech Project Leader. You do not have to have any prior ASUC experience, just a passion for driving results and making an impact on our community. 

 

If you’re interested in applying, we encourage you to check out the office guide (tinyurl.com/mchenoffice) and the application link (tinyurl.com/mchenfall20app). If you have any questions feel free to reach out to mchen@asuc.org
history.subject: Apply to be a Tech/Data Science Director or CivTech Project Leader
